My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 10

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

It's back to Victoria as best mates, Harry and Christo prepare to serve up their menu. Having known each other since birth, they hope to make their own mark in the kitchen but will it be a success?
